Class WorkspaceChangeEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      domosaics.ui.workspace.components.WorkspaceChangeEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class WorkspaceChangeEvent
extends java.util.EventObject

WorkspaceChangeEvent describes events which are fired to registered listeners, when an workspace element changed.

Author:
Andreas Held
